keyFacts: The document is a travel voucher approval for an Epstein investigation-related witness interview trip.
The trip occurred from February 19-20, 2020 to Pensacola, Florida.
The voucher total expenses were $628.07 with an estimated trip cost of $973.89.
The document reference is R20NYS13403 - Epstein Investigation - Witness interview.
This shows ongoing investigative activity related to the Epstein case in February 2020.
